&WChangelog (02/26/21)&n

- Druids (a type of cleric) now have second attack
- Using "mstand" with no target now forces ALL mounts you own to stand
- The "Aid" spell now restores HP equal to what it grants
- New characters will now have a map of Sanction instead of Karthay
- Fixed a bug with the "mount" command
- Other misc. Imm-related fixes/updates

